HEADWORD: Curmurring
<hw>Cur*mur"ring</hw> <pr>(k?r-m?r"r?ng)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>Murmuring; grumbling; -- sometimes applied to the rumbling produced
by a slight attack of the gripes.</def> <mark>[Scot.]</mark>
